    "order": 8,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Bushwick Central + Knickerbocker — Ecuadorian night vendors + a taco cart with the best salsa in the city.",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-01T19:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "be2f7cbd32fd5f61754b2915115c9f107",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T00:00:00Z",
    "order": 9,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Editorial angle",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-01T20:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b8bea3e31ab2f18ff2b9d1a94c4d2a35a",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T01:00:00Z",
    "order": 10,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Not a survey. Six markets, one photographer, warm-light aesthetic in a cold-color palette (blues + reds). The pitch: Brooklyn/Queens night food is a New York story, not a novelty. Edgewater Food Journal is the lead target; Grub Street secondary.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-01T21:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bd9376b22abc407124646925b7b579ee4",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T02:00:00Z",
    "order": 11,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Shot list template per market",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-01T22:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b35247b305fb5919eef41dc8c5ee30277",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T03:00:00Z",
    "order": 12,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Establishing wide — the block at peak activity.",
    "type": "numbered_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-01T23:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b54f1bb5d15c11ddb08c76a1efaa75bf3",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T04:00:00Z",
    "order": 13,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Two portraits — one vendor, one customer.",
    "type": "numbered_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T00:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b2450a7a382bcf476e89ab406cb4f7b8a",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T05:00:00Z",
    "order": 14,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "One-plate hero — signature dish.",
    "type": "numbered_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T01:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bcb95fcd422aacf0b100941a077387a20",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T06:00:00Z",
    "order": 15,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Three details — steam, spice grinder, hand-off.",
    "type": "numbered_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T02:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b18d39df99152793cee1bbfb860951cfa",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T07:00:00Z",
    "order": 16,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "One long-exposure — signage + motion blur through the frame.",
    "type": "numbered_list_item"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T03:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bb8cb8b4f4c227100eff4d79377f02632",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T08:00:00Z",
    "order": 17,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Gear notes",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T04:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b9b386debc64c6c7f45a59e76bc8b9f09",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T09:00:00Z",
    "order": 18,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Sony A7IV + 24-70 f/2.8 as the workhorse. 90mm macro for the hero plates. One Profoto B10 with a small softbox for cold-weather portraits when ambient is too low. Skip the second body — running-and-gunning solo.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T05:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "b90ec4bacd93d2781e7ed9d54d0f03021",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T10:00:00Z",
    "order": 19,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Post workflow",
    "type": "heading_2"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T06:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bdb32377387b919cf0b54e15d80577e4c",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T11:00:00Z",
    "order": 20,
    "page_id": "p7f5d96f0ade3620917e4000e3d150f19",
    "parent_block_id": null,
    "text": "Backup to external SSD before leaving the market. First cull in Capture One same night. Retouch in Lightroom over two days. Deliver Dropbox link watermarked.",
    "type": "paragraph"
  },
  {
    "checked": null,
    "created_time": "2026-11-02T07:00:00Z",
    "has_children": "false",
    "id": "bee9e83b05f525b3ca3e3256adb147711",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-10-02T12:00:00Z",
    "order": 21,
    "page_id": "pe0d17360314901268d70278a556d2d7c",
    "parent_block_id": null,
